    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jung-Kuei Yang</b>\n</p><p><b>Jung-Kuei Yang</b>,<br />\na Taiwanese computer scientist at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lan_Yang_Institute_of_Technology\">Lan Yang Institute of Technology</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toucheng,_Yilan\">Toucheng, Yilan</a>. \nHe works and published on <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> techniques  and <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">Monte-Carlo tree search</a> applied to <a href=\"/Connect6\" title=\"Connect6\">Connect6</a>. He is primary author of the <a href=\"/Connect6\" title=\"Connect6\">Connect6</a> program <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=507\">Kavalan</a>,\nwhich won the <a href=\"/index.php?title=21st_Computer_Olympiad&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"21st Computer Olympiad (page does not exist)\">21st Computer Olympiad 2018</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jung-Kuei_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jung-Kuei_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>The Bitboard Design and Bitwise Computing in Connect Six</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#GPW\" title=\"Conferences\">14th Game Programming Workshop</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jung-Kuei_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Searching-for-Stage-Proof-Number-in-Connect6-Yen-Yang/2de70372893e8773b12391f75d2b964ea7fb6df2\">Searching for Stage Proof Number in Connect6</a></i>. <a href=\"/index.php?title=TAAI_2010&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"TAAI 2010 (page does not exist)\">TAAI 2010</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Two-Stage Monte Carlo Tree Search for Connect6</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOCIAIGAMES\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computational Intelligence and AI in Games</a>, Vol. 3, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a>, <a href=\"/Kuo-Yuan_Kao\" title=\"Kuo-Yuan Kao\">Kuo-Yuan Kao</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tai-Ning_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tai-Ning Yang (page does not exist)\">Tai-Ning Yang</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0950705112001293\">Bitboard Knowledge Base System and Elegant Search Architectures for Connect6</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knowledge-Based_Systems_(journal)\">Knowledge-Based Systems</a>, Vol. 34</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tsan-Cheng_Su&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tsan-Cheng Su (page does not exist)\">Tsan-Cheng Su</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>TCGA 2012 Computer Games Tournament. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#35_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 35, No. 3</a></i></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/t/Tseng:Ping=Jung\">Ping-Jung Tseng</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/6783902\">Bitboard Connection Code Design for Connect6</a></i>. <a href=\"/index.php?title=TAAI_2013&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"TAAI 2013 (page does not exist)\">TAAI 2013</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i>Building Connect6 opening by using the Monte Carlo tree search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/icaci/icaci2016.html\">ICACI 2016</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>Kavalan wins Connect6 tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#41_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 41, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=21st_Computer_Olympiad&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"21st Computer Olympiad (page does not exist)\">21st Computer Olympiad 2018</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jung-Kuei_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jung-Kuei Yang</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a> (<b>2020</b>). <i>The Connect6 tournament of the 2019 Computer Olympiad</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#42_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 42, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=22nd_Computer_Olympiad&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"22nd Computer Olympiad (page does not exist)\">22nd Computer Olympiad</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jung-Kuei_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=501\">Jung-Kuei Yang's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jung-Kuei_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/y/Yang:Jung=Kuei.html\">dblp: Jung-Kuei Yang</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301023104\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 41/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 78/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6389-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301023104 and revision id 19789\n -->\n"
